sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>AlertDetailPage
    participant API1 as DRF<br/>BlockIPView
    participant API2 as DRF<br/>UnblockIPView
    participant SER as BlockIPActionSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Click "Block IP" on alert
    FE->>API1: POST /api/alerts/{alert_id}/block/
    API1->>SER: BlockIPActionSerializer.validate(data)
    API1->>DB: Alert.objects.get(pk=alert_id)
    DB-->>API1: Alert instance
    API1->>DB: BlockedIP.objects.create(ip=alert.source_ip, reason)
    DB-->>API1: BlockedIP created
    API1-->>FE: 201 Created {blocked_ip}
    FE-->>U: Show "IP Blocked" confirmation
    Note over U,FE: Later, user wants to unblock
    U->>FE: Click "Unblock IP" on alert
    FE->>API2: POST /api/alerts/{alert_id}/unblock/
    API2->>DB: BlockedIP.objects.filter(ip=alert.source_ip).delete()
    DB-->>API2: Deleted
    API2-->>FE: 200 OK "IP unblocked"
    FE-->>U: Show "IP Unblocked" confirmation
